{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-8","id":"msg_018VvU5mEBmfsGzCGpuZHiFL","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01Cqv62Bcx76HyG3WkCXyGLB","name":"Bash","input":{"command":"cat > submit.txt <<'EOF'\nMongoDB replica set upgrade 5.0.5 -> 6.0.5 complete.\n\nSteps performed:\n1. Verified preconditions: 3-member RS (mongodb-replica-0/1/2) healthy on mongo:5.0.5,\n   FCV=5.0 (required baseline for a 6.0 upgrade). Auth user: admin-user/admin@admin db.\n2. Snapshotted data: testdb.data = 1 document.\n3. Rolling upgrade via `kubectl set image statefulset/mongodb-replica mongod=mongo:6.0.5`.\n   StatefulSet RollingUpdate updates pods in reverse ordinal (2->1->0), upgrading\n   secondaries first and the primary last; a clean election occurred (primary moved to pod-2).\n4. Waited for rollout to complete; all 3 pods Ready on mongo:6.0.5, RS health=1 on all members.\n5. Finalized feature compatibility on the primary: setFeatureCompatibilityVersion(\"6.0\").\n\nFinal state:\n- All members: version 6.0.5, FCV 6.0, health 1 (1 PRIMARY + 2 SECONDARY).\n- Data preserved: testdb.data still 1 document, unchanged.\n- No operators/CRDs used; plain StatefulSet rolling update.\nEOF\necho written; pwd","description":"Write submit.txt"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":2,"cache_creation_input_tokens":704,"cache_read_input_tokens":34826,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":704},"output_tokens":3,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"d49a1787-b36c-40da-930b-333e2fd2dd2f","uuid":"92cdf3c3-b044-4c0f-b80e-f8b0d109a135","request_id":"req_011CcAwQUtxkUSwsaX5QBYj9"}
